<br>
When I finally convinced by best buddy Iluvatar to transfer here from CT, he was very pleased. He often told me how odd he thought it was that there was so little animosity among the guilds, and overall how mature the majority of people were.<br>
<br>
Bear in mind that this is a guy that has been playing on one of the original servers since the first week of EQ. He said he's been happier on MT then he ever was on CT.<br>
<br>
I think that says a lot, personally. I am proud that I am one of the many that helped lay the cornerstones of this server's foundation, and all of you who still play should be proud that you have done so well in maintaining that foundation. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Argond Valiantfist</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Grandmaster Geezer of Morell-Thule</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=133460" target="top">Geezer-gear</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#0E0E0E><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=faate>Faate</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Egging EW</span><br>  Posts: 411<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(10/15/03 2:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1921.topic&index=34>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The low end of the game</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> IV left the server en masse to go to the new server opening up, Thoxule Paells<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
