and lest we forget... United Ale Drinkers!!!  They would host PvP competition in Freeport in the arena.  Then the winners of all levels would get drunk off Elven wine and fight to the finish...  Damn good times, the 1st time I ever wanted to forego a saturday afternoon at the beach instead to sit and play this game.  ...wait a minute... DAMN YOU UAD's!!!<br>
