Utanalia was the guildleader when I joined my original char (on my 1st account) July 2000, when everyone in Neriak was either Reapers of Sorrow or Order of the White Hand.  Cynful and Ravensky came over to MT later... <br>
<br>
Until Xxein's last days of playing and the decision to let <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Hall of Heroes</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> die... it was the longest active guild on the server - that kept the same name and didn't reform.  That is what was posted on these boards around last year when this topic came up.<br>
